item.title: Shrooms
item.dc:creator: @kurt pixels
item.description:
@kurt wrote:

[quote=“jme_009, post:17, topic:132317”][quote author=wixter link=topic=183287.msg1680524#msg1680524 date=1187331450]

I smoke weed, but more often than not i have skunk. I wouldnt ever have pot, dealers often fill pot with things like old plastic, tires, old rubber ect. This adds weight and price to the bag. So really when you smoke pot, your smoking shit.

Get a better source then. I buy straight from respected growers. Easier said then done I guess, all depends where you live.

Lol…Hmmmm The farthest i would ever go tho is pot lol

Oh, sorry if it sounded like I was pressuring you to try it. If your not ready to try it, then trying it would be a huge mistake. They pack a powerful punch that you may not expect and a very intense feeling.

Yeh , alot of the pot here in england, or maybe just in my area, is full of shit.
[/quote]

Ah, yeah I’ve been hearing a lot of bad stuff about englands pot recently.

I’m from Canada, everyone is a farmer around here :P[/quote]

I’m from Alaska, weed is almost legal here

Shrooms are the funniest drug I’ve ever done though the best high…

Coke and weed have nothing on shrooms…

Although you do feel safer when you’re high on weed compared to shrooms… hahah but shrooms are my fav fav

item.title: Shrooms
item.dc:creator: @jme jme
item.description:
@jme wrote:

Cunit:

I only Smoke (cigs not pot) but what i herd they make you feel like shit after comming down… Dont know if its right but wont wana find out

I’ve heard of that, but so far I haven’t experienced that and neither have my friends(or at least no complaints…)

However during the rather long comeup I feel some minor stomach discomfort. Smoking a little bit of pot gets rid of it entirely.

A 2 gram dose of cubensis is the sweet spot for me. Although I enjoy hallucinations, they are quite minimal however I just feel so amazing and I cannot stop laughing the entire time. The way I think is so weird too, I examine everything and take note of all it’s detail. I talk to random people and it’s just weird lol.
